{"tid":1544354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又整合] 證人已共同指出831有一名嘔白泡者，係消防抬走，根本冇送過院","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:53:07.000Z","uid":161430,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c6709f5d4e946aaef84e390825c8bfa519c583c5","tid":1544354,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"網上爆料者2名 (最早出現)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zUGzpUt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUGzpUt.png&h=1e2ab0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者會企出黎既龍小姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6W8NPnT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6W8NPnT.png&h=650cd1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他證人: 太子站手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3pJnJe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3pJnJe.png&h=f0683315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJko69U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJko69U.png&h=88e2424e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然要講，佢地 = / = fact check，<br />\n但不同人都講出一致細節，龍小姐更係出記者會度講。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>證人講既野都有以下共通點，由此得知:</strong></ins><br />\n1. 現場有一位不省人事 被叫「唔好訓」既嘔白泡既市民，佢情況最危殆<br />\n2. 係由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>消防抬走，根本就冇送過去醫院</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&darr;</strong><br />\n<br />\n- 因此<span style=\"color: red;\">即時送院既7人名單裡，其實根本冇包括過呢位冇曬反應 (甚至被形容係即場犧牲) 既市民</span><br />\n- 所以佢其實現時係徹底失蹤，去向不明，HA官方資料，理論上根本唔會有佢名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQTaKiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQTaKiB.jpg&h=dc26b083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 當然，亦有人提及，醫護界係收到消息，知有市民犧牲左<br />\n(但唔等如話佢有被送去醫院，醫護只係講緊佢地有高層收到風，兩者冇衝突)<br />\n<br />\n- 亦有可能推測因為死既人唔止一位 (嘔白泡者以外)，因此有人係送到醫院後先離逝，因此醫護界知有人犧牲<br />\n- 一直有流傳一開始講10人，後來變7人，實際上有3人死亡<br />\n<br />\n以上為少少最新update資料。"},{"pid":"357ffe02c06a131ba520dea7114b37d79e3d18fc","tid":1544354,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警還命"},{"pid":"7c1b1bf9f53f45d13b433e179205bc6e437ce450","tid":1544354,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"038b24b5b6c193b4e75f0ff9a12aed2237075154","tid":1544354,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0a748c7b82e84d1d69c7d9591f75ae78578168f","tid":1544354,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGZQNpw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGZQNpw.png&h=a7a77059&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aG8NPCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaG8NPCX.jpg&h=ca416e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzuxghY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzuxghY.jpg&h=e89ed136&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uL23nXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuL23nXY.jpg&h=1912fb66&s={SIZE}\" /><img s